20pay%20the%20fees%20to%20complete%20the%20transfer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECollins%20thinks%20it's%20a%20win-win%3A%20The%20buyer%20gets%20a%20cheap%20house%2C%20and%20she%20hopes%20to%20make%20more%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Imelda%20Collins%2C%20who%20is%20selling%20her%20house%20in%20Ireland%20via%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fraffall.com%2F364020%2Fenter-raffle-to-win-a-stunning-home-on-175-acres-near-sligo-ireland-hosted-by-imelda-collins%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ean%20online%20raffle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Each%20entry%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3E5%20%3Cem%3Eeuros%20(about%20%246.75)%2C%20and%20people%20can%20buy%20multiple%20entries.%20The%20drawing%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Thursday%2C%20May%2022%2C%20at%2010%20a.m.%20local%20time.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20from%20Ireland%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20is%20from%20Italy.%20We've%20lived%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20for%20a%20number%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20I%20bought%20this%20home%20near%20Manorhamilton%2C%20a%20small%20town%20about%2020%20minutes%20east%20of%20Sligo%2C%20because%20we%20were%20going%20to%20stay%20in%20Ireland%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20window%20looking%20out%20on%20the%20Irish%20countryside%20silver-colored%20is%20set%20in%20a%20green%20wall%20above%20a%20kitchen%20sink%20and%20between%20two%20white%20cabinets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682deaf7ac40ae2b0c9ea62a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20two-bedroom%20house%20on%201.75%20acres.%20I%20paid%20%E2%82%AC133%2C000%20(about%20%24150%2C000)%2C%20which%20was%20well%20over%20asking%2C%20but%20that's%20just%20what%20the%20market%20was.%20I%20estimate%20I%20put%20about%20%E2%82%AC150%2C000%20(%24170%2C000)%20into%20the%20home%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20we%20completely%20gutted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20is%20just%20stunning.%20It%20has%20the%20most%20amazing%20views%20and%20mountains%20all%20around.%20We're%20on%20a%20countryside%20road%2C%20and%20I%20barely%20see%20three%20cars%20a%20day.%20I%20love%20hearing%20birdsong.%20I%20love%20how%20we're%20out%20in%20the%20country%20but%20still%20so%20close%20to%20a%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225897%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20of%20a%20red%20front%20door%20and%20the%20home's%20entryway%2C%20with%20flowered%20wallpaper%20and%20art%20on%20the%20walls%20leading%20to%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682ded09c6ad288d148186d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223931%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entryway.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20our%20situation%20has%20changed.%20My%20heart%20is%20in%20Italy.%20My%20husband's%20family%20is%20in%20Italy.%20I%20got%20used%20to%20living%20there%2C%20with%20the%20amazing%20food%2C%20weather%2C%20and%20wine.%20That's%20where%20we%20belong%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20property%20in%20Ireland%3B%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20homes%20for%20sale.%20It%20took%20me%20years%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20really%20nice%20to%20give%20somebody%20the%20opportunity%20to%20win%20a%20home%20for%20the%20price%20of%20a%20latte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231f0be68-08e9-4059-aa0d-242189239d30%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHolding%20a%20raffle%20to%20sell%20my%20home%20seemed%20like%20a%20win%20for%20both%20me%20and%20the%20buyer%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20read%20online%20about%20a%20lady%20in%20Dublin%20who%20raffled%20off%20her%20apartment%20because%20she%20was%20moving%20to%20Paris.%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20kind%20of%20similar%20to%20my%20situation.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20so%20this%20has%20been%20taking%20shape%20for%20a%20while.%20She's%20the%20one%20who%20showed%20me%20the%20Raffall%20platform%20for%20raffles%20and%20explained%20what%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelling%20it%20the%20normal%20route%20would%20be%20easier%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20cool%20idea%20and%20wanted%20to%20try%20something%20new.%20Also%2C%20if%20the%20raffle%20succeeds%2C%20I%20hope%20to%20make%20more%20money%20than%20if%20I%20sold%20it%20traditionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20today's%20market%2C%20I%20would%20expect%20to%20get%20around%20%E2%82%AC300%2C000%20(%24340%2C000).%20It's%20so%20hard%20to%20predict%20an%20exact%20figure%2C%20but%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20where%20I'd%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20single-story%20house%20with%20red%20doors%20and%20red%20window%20shutters%20called%20Butterfly%20Cottage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682deb0068a292900801e89b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20house%20Collins%20is%20raffling%20off.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20costs%20associated%20with%20the%20raffle.%20I've%20paid%20a%20marketing%20professional%20to%20help%20me%2C%20I've%20run%20national%20ads%20in%20newspapers%20for%20seven%20weeks%2C%20I've%20paid%20for%20a%20photographer%20and%20drone%20videographer.%20Then%2C%20when%20it's%20all%20done%2C%20Raffall%20will%20take%2010%25%20commission%20on%20all%20the%20sales%20as%20well.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20all%20that%2C%20I%20expect%20to%20come%20in%20higher.%20Some%20people%20don't%20understand%20all%20those%20costs%20and%20just%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20she's%20sold%20150%2C000%20tickets%2C%20so%20she'll%20be%20taking%20in%20%E2%82%AC900%2C000.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20that%20simple.%20%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20Collins%20declined%20to%20share%20exactly%20how%20much%20she%20spent%20promoting%20the%20raffle.%20She%20also%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20many%20people%20had%20entered%2C%20but%20as%20of%201%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20May%2023%2C%20298%2C624%20paid%20and%20free%20tickets%20had%20been%20issued%2C%20according%20to%20Raffall.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20laid%20out%20all%20the%20costs%20on%20my%20website.%20I'm%20paying%20for%20the%20legal%20fees%20associated%20with%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20property%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yellow%20patio%20table%20with%20orange%20chairs%20sits%20on%20a%20patio%20surrounded%20by%20a%20white%20fence%20with%20the%20Irish%20countryside%20in%20the%20distance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682deaf7c6ad288d14818662%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20patio.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20the%20winner%20to%20just%20pay%20the%20ticket%20for%20the%20home.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20extra%20costs%20whatsoever%20to%20the%20winner%20%E2%80%94%20none.%20I%20just%20thought%20that%20was%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226525d7ec-8cdb-430b-9fad-f36233a3e647%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20raffle%20has%20taken%20over%20my%20life%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20the%20adventure%20of%20a%20lifetime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lady%20who%20raffled%20off%20her%20Dublin%20apartment%20told%20me%20the%20process%20would%20take%20over%20my%20entire%20life%2C%20and%20she%20was%20right.%20Sometimes%20it's%20caused%20me%20great%20stress.%20In%20the%20evenings%2C%20I%20come%20home%20from%20work%20and%20then%20I'm%20on%20the%20laptop%20for%20a%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%2Fdining%20room%20with%20a%20vaulted%20ceiling%2C%20colorful%20wallpaper%2C%20a%20couch%2C%20and%20a%20dining%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682deaf768a292900801e897%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%2Fdining%20room.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20I've%20been%20researching%20ways%20to%20get%20the%20word%20out%2C%20pitching%20myself%20to%20local%20newspapers%20in%20Ireland%20and%20the%20UK.%20I've%20joined%20Facebook%20groups%20where%20I%20thought%20there'd%20be%20interest%2C%20like%20one%20for%20Americans%20moving%20to%20Ireland.%20I%20even%20did%20research%20on%20where%20the%20most%20Irish%20descendants%20were%20in%20the%20US%20to%20target%20those%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20enter%20the%20raffle%20from%20wherever%20you%20are%20as%20long%20as%20it's%20legal%20in%20your%20country.%20I%20can%20only%20see%20names%20on%20the%20Raffall%20page%2C%20not%20nationalities.%20But%20I%20know%20that%20I've%20been%20featured%20in%20the%20New%20Zealand%20press.%20It's%20so%20fantastic%20to%20see%20the%20word%20is%20spreading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bedroom%20with%20pink%20walls%20and%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20flowered%20bedspread%2C%20with%20a%20nightstand%20to%20one%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682dec8668a292900801e8e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20primary%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20overwhelming.%20Before%20the%20raffle%2C%20I%20was%20never%20in%20the%20media.%20I%20was%20never%20even%20on%20social%20media.%20I%20will%20be%20happy%20for%20it%20to%20come%20to%20an%20end.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20seven%20months%2C%20