5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20Action%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20how%20companies%20are%20implementing%20AI%20innovations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20companies%20look%20to%20AI%20for%20increases%20in%20productivity%2C%20some%20employees%20are%20wary.%20They%20worry%20about%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-ladder-software-engineers-collapsing-ai-google-meta-coding-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20lost%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-creative-process-storytellers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20diminished%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-ethics-risks-responsibility-business-bcg-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ethical%20oversteps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leaving%20many%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-broken-career-ladder-gen-z-entry-level-jobs-ai-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20repelled%20by%20daily%20AI%20use%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPinterest%2C%20a%20social%20media%20company%20with%20about%204%2C700%20employees%2C%20has%20sought%20to%20address%20such%20concerns%20by%20keeping%20employees%20closely%20involved%20in%20the%20development%20of%20internal%20AI%20tools%20so%20those%20tools%20are%20viewed%20as%20efficient%20and%20helpful%2C%20not%20just%20mandated%20from%20the%20top%20down.%20Key%20toward%20this%20mission%20has%20been%20Pinterest's%20annual%20Makeathon%2C%20which%20is%20in%20its%2014th%20year.%20The%20employee-led%20competition%20used%20to%20be%20viewed%20mostly%20as%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20recommend%20fixes%2C%20said%20Anirudh%20Koul%2C%20Pinterest's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-using-ai-bain-survey-roi-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20tech%20lead.%20Now%2C%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20its%20usefulness%20has%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overarching%20goal%20is%20ground-up%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Koul%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20that%20if%20we%20can%20give%20the%20employees%20the%20opportunity%20and%20freedom%20to%20tell%20us%20what%20must%20be%20done%2C%20and%20give%20them%20some%20space%20to%20showcase%20working%20proof%20of%20their%20concept%2C%20we%20might%20find%20new%20innovations%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225084a548-b033-4e6d-9e66-0e7138fc42b9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20Pinterest's%20companywide%20hackathon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMakeathon%20is%20Pinterest's%20version%20of%20a%20hackathon%20%E2%80%94%20an%20event%20at%20which%20people%20work%20together%20to%20create%20new%20software%20quickly.%20Hackathons%20are%20designed%20to%20spark%20new%20ideas%20and%20increase%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prevent-employee-skepticism-push-back-gen-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20employee%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Brandon%20Kessler%20of%20Devpost%2C%20a%20digital%20platform%20for%20running%20hackathons.%20Since%202022's%20AI%20boom%2C%20hackathon%20demand%20has%20exploded%2C%20Kessler%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20hackathons'%20appeal%2C%20Kessler%20said%20the%20events%20%26quot%3Bget%20people%20excited%20because%20they%20get%20to%20build%20something%20they%20want%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%2C%20'Hey%2C%20all%2C%20please%20use%20this%20tool.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20people%20learning%20these%20new%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bbuilding%20stuff%20that%20helps%20the%20business%2C%20and%20collaborating%20and%20having%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20all%20within%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPinterest%20employees%20witnessed%20this%20type%20of%20quick%20development%20in%20early%202023%2C%20just%20a%20few%20months%20after%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E's%20release.%20Pinterest's%20senior%20director%20of%20engineering%2C%20Anthony%20Suarez%2C%20helped%20collect%20a%20handful%20of%20engineers%20to%20have%20a%20mini%20hackathon%20which%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20internal%20chatbot%20tool.%20By%20their%20official%20Makeathon%20in%20July%2C%20Pinterest's%20now-foundational%20plug-in%20AI%20system%20was%20ready%20for%20wider%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Pinterest%2C%20hackathon%20projects%20start%20at%20an%20internal%20company%20page%20where%20employees%20across%20departments%20can%20log%20pitches.%20In%20the%20week%20before%20Makeathon%2C%20Koul's%20team%20hosts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-will-change-most-jobs-employers-help-workers-keep-up-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20generative%20AI%20works%20and%20how%20to%20write%20prompts.%20There's%20also%20a%20class%20on%20no-code%20tools%20for%20app%20building%20so%20that%20nontechnical%20employees%20can%20still%20employ%20AI%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20teams%20from%20across%20departments%20form%20around%20an%20idea.%20Suarez%20collaborated%20with%20seven%20Makeathon%20teams%20last%20cycle%2C%20mostly%20composed%20of%20fellow%20employees%20he%20had%20never%20worked%20with%20before.%20They%20also%20have%20the%20support%20of%20Koul's%20%26quot%3Bhack%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20support%20staff%20who%20work%20across%20the%20company%20and%20specialize%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20engineering%2C%20design%2C%20and%20video%20editing.%20The%20hack%20doctors%20help%20refine%20ideas%20and%20prepare%20teams%20to%20take%20questions%20from%20executives.%20Last%20year%2C%20just%20under%2094%25%20of%20teams%20worked%20with%20a%20hack%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20usually%20find%20that%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20participants%20are%20actually%20not%20from%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20Koul%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20pair%20up%20with%20engineers%20to%20bring%20their%20ideas%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20We've%20had%20teams%20where%20people%20from%20six%20different%20countries%20come%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20team%20produces%20a%20video%20pitch%2C%20which%20colleagues%20up%20to%20the%20executive%20level%20can%20watch%20and%20vote%20on.%20Makeathon%20is%20strategically%20scheduled%20for%20late%20summer%20so%20any%20resulting%20tools%20can%20be%20incorporated%20into%20Pinterest's%20companywide%20planning%20period%20in%20September%20and%20October%2C%20Suarez%20told%20BI.%20He%20estimated%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20these%20Makeathon%20projects%20get%20funded%20during%20this%20cycle%20and%20called%20the%20event%20an%20%26quot%3Binnovation%20flywheel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260b040fc-d8cb-4348-beb5-24a68ae3add0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20a%20Makeathon%20idea%20becomes%20an%20AI-tool%20reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202023%20Makeathon%2C%20one%20of%20Pinterest's%20sales%20employees%20had%20an%20idea%3A%20What%20if%20AI%20could%20collect%20and%20search%20through%20all%20the%20company's%20internal%20documents%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sales%20employee%20recruited%20a%2014-person%20team%2C%20including%20Charlie%20Gu%2C%20a%20senior%20engineering%20manager%20on%20Pinterest's%20data%20team.%20Gu%20said%20he%20envisioned%20the%20tool%20as%20a%20Slack-based%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatbots-talking-ai-robot-chat-machine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20employees%20could%20turn%20to%20instead%20of%20bugging%20their%20colleagues.%20The%20team%20knew%2C%20however%2C%20that%20some%20existing%20documentation%20wouldn't%20be%20up%20to%20date%20when%20the%20chatbot%20pulled%20it%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20up%20with%20a%20system%20where%20you%20can%20report%20answers%20and%20create%20new%20documentation%20on%20the%20fly%2C%26quot%3B%20Gu%20said.%20The%20team%20pitched%2C%20built%2C%20and%20eventually%20implemented%20the%20document%20finder%20across%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20now%20answers%2C%20on%20average%2C%20an%20estimated%204%2C000%20questions%20a%20month%2C%20according%20to%20Pinterest.%20The%20tool%20was%20also%20designed%20to%20access%20thousands%20of%20internal%20documents%20from%20Google%20Docs%2C%20Slack%20threads%2C%20and%20slide%20decks%2C%20said%20Koul%2C%20who%20is%20quite%20passionate%20about%20Makeathon.%20(He%20called%20over%20shaky%20service%20at%20a%20Mount%20Everest%20base%20camp%20to%20rave%20about%20it.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMakeathon%20also%20encouraged%20some%20employees%20to%20come%20up%20with%20useful%20AI%20prompts.%20In%202024%2C%20Koul's%20team%20posed%20a%20challenge%3A%20Who%20could%20come%20up%20with%20the%20best%20questions%20to%20get%20Pinterest's%20chatbot%20to%20produce%20the%20most%20accurate%20and%20precise%20answers%3F%20Gu%20said%20that%20they%20had%20about%20200%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20employees'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-get-better-chatgpt-ai-prompt-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprompt%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20with%20Pinterest's%20overall%20goal%20of%20encouraging%20employee%20engagement%20with%20AI.%20The%20effort%20also%20led%20Pinterest%20to%20integrate%20AI%20agents%20into%20the%20process%20of%20writing%20more%20precise%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20internal%20company%20surveys%2C%2096%25%20of%20Suarez's%20team%20of%20more%20than%2060%20use%20generative%20AI%20every%20month%2C%20and%2078%25%20of%20the%20company's%201%2C800%20engineers%20report%20time%20savings%20from%20using%20internal%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuarez%20said%20he'd%20been%20%26quot%3Bquite%20surprised%20by%20the%20positive%20feel%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20tools%20across%20the%20business%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BPart%20of%20that%20is%2C%20we%20didn't%20force%20adoption%20of%20these%20tools%20early%20on%2C%20and%20we%20still%20aren't%20saying%2C%20'You%20have%20to%20do%20this.'%20We're%20trying%20to%20come%20at%20this%20more%20from%20creating%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpinterest-hackathons-makeathon-employees-lead-generative-ai-tools-innovation-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747843126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682b55f2c6ad288d14814f38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpinterest-hackathons-makeathon-employees-lead-generative-ai-tools-innovation-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pinterest's%20annual%20Makeathon%20is%20designed%20to%20foster%20new%20ideas%2C%20including%20for%20AI%20tools%20that%20could%20increase%20productivity%20across%20the%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpinterest-hackathons-makeathon-employees-lead-generative-ai-tools-innovation-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%20a%20month%20in%20Turkey%20with%20friends.%20Our%20trip%20was%20great%2C%20but%20would've%20been%20better%20if%20we'd%20avoided%20these%205%20mistakes.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20women%20sitting%20on%20stone%20wall%20in%20Turkey%20staring%20out%20into%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236c433fe8d3928365b33d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20learned%20a%20lot%20and%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes%20during%20our%20girls'%20trip%20to%20Turkey.%20%3Cp%3EAlison%20Kaplan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20spent%20a%20month%20in%20Turkey%20with%20a%20group%20of%20friends.%20We%20had%20fun%2C%20but%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20didn't%20realize%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuse-layover-explore-fail-visa-rules-american-istanbul-2025-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIstanbul%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20two%20international%20airports%20or%20that%20%C3%A7ay%20had%20so%20much%20caffeine.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20wish%20I%20hadn't%20exchanged%20my%20currency%20in%20the%20airport%20or%20bought%20so%20many%20souvenirs%20at%20Grand%20Bazaar.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%2C%20I%20went%20on%20a%20monthlong%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperfect-48-hours-las-vegas-girls-trip-itinerary-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egirls'%20trip%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Turkey.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20we%20left%2C%20I%20spent%20many%20evenings%20researching%20must-see%20attractions%2C%20searching%20for%20cute%20lodging%20options%2C%20and%20maintaining%20my%20Diamond%20League%20status%20learning%20Turkish%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fduolingo-ceo-criteria-new-subjects-added-chess-music-language-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDuolingo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20preparations%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20great%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20but%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes%20that%20we'll%20be%20sure%20to%20avoid%20next%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20didn't%20realize%20there%20was%20more%20than%20one%20major%20airport%20in%20Istanbul.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20Turkey%2C%20Istanbul%2C%20Ataturk%20airport%2C%20people%20looking%20at%20departure%20sign%2C%20standing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236b4e68a2929008012b19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20there%20was%20only%20one%20international%20airport%20in%20Istanbul.%3Cp%3Ealeks333%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIstanbul%20is%20the%20biggest%20city%20I've%20ever%20visited%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20so%20large%20that%20it%20actually%20hosts%20two%20international%20airports.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIstanbul%20Airport%20(IST)%20is%20on%20the%20European%20side%20of%20the%20city%20and%20Sabiha%20G%C3%B6k%C3%A7en%20International%20Airport%20(SAW)%20is%20on%20the%20Asian%20side.%20It%20can%20take%20about%20two%20hours%20to%20get%20from%20one%20airport%20to%20the%20other%20by%20bus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20friends%20and%20I%20all%20flew%20into%20IST%2C%20but%20some%20of%20our%20group%20booked%20domestic%20flights%20out%20of%20SAW%20the%20following%20morning%20without%20realizing%20it%20was%20a%20different%20airport%20in%20Istanbul.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20all%20made%20our%20flights%2C%20but%20we%20had%20to%20split%20up%20into%20different%20hotels%20during%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstayed-in-small-hotel-inside-airport-during-layover-yotelair-istanbul-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIstanbul%20layover%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20one%20near%20IST%20and%20one%20near%20SAW.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20shouldn't%20have%20exchanged%20my%20money%20at%20the%20airport.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkish%20liras%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236bb668a2929008012b32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20plenty%20of%20places%20for%20me%20to%20exchange%20my%20currency.%20%3Cp%3EAndrzej%20Rostek%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20I%20arrived%20in%20Istanbul%20was%20after%20business%20hours%2C%20I%20figured%20my%20best%20option%20was%20to%20exchange%20US%20dollars%20for%20liras%20at%20the%20airport%20despite%20the%20poor%20exchange%20rate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eit%20seemed%20like%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20enter%20a%20new%20city%20without%20any%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20regretted%20my%20decision%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20left%20the%20airport%20and%20found%20that%20many%20exchange%20counters%20in%20the%20city%20were%20open%20late%20%E2%80%94%20and%20had%20better%20rates.%20It%20was%20also%20easy%20to%20find%20ATMs%20throughout%20the%20trip.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20that%20first%20money%20mishap%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20I%20got%20all%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eliras%3Cspan%3E%20from%20Halkbank%20ATMs%2C%20which%20didn't%20charge%20me%20fees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20took%20me%20too%20long%20to%20realize%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20local%20drinks%20is%20packed%20with%20caffeine.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20with%20dessert%20and%20coffee%20in%20cafe%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236bd9c6ad288d1480c936%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223099%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHad%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20caffeine%20was%20in%20the%20tea%2C%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20drank%20so%20much%20of%20it%20each%20day.%3Cp%3EAlison%20Kaplan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurkish%20tea%2C%20or%20%26quot%3B%C3%A7ay%26quot%3B%20(pronounced%20like%20%26quot%3Bchai%26quot%3B)%2C%20is%20a%20popular%20drink%20in%20Turkey%2C%20and%20sharing%20tea%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20Turkish%20culture.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20my%20first%20few%20days%20in%20Turkey%2C%20I%20accepted%20tea%20whenever%20it%20was%20offered.%20It%20was%20inexpensive%20and%20delicious%2C%20and%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20participate%20in%20local%20rituals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20offered%20the%20tea%20at%20restaurants%2C%20shops%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20dentist's%20office%20(I%20was%20there%20for%20a%20bit%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-medical-tourism-turkey-saved-money-dental-work-tooth-surgery-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedical%20tourism%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20realize%20at%20first%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20%C3%A7ay%20is%20pretty%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ecaffeinated%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20brew%2C%20an%20average%20cup%20can%20contain%20over%2040%20milligrams%20of%20caffeine%20%E2%80%94%20about%20half%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaffeine-daily-serving-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecaffeine%20in%20a%20standard%20cup%20of%20coffee%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20I%20registered%20how%20much%20caffeine%20I'd%20been%20drinking%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20I%20understood%20why%20my%20jet%20lag%20was%20so%20much%20worse%20than%20usual.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ended%20up%20overpaying%20for%20souvenirs%20at%20the%20famous%20Grand%20Bazaar.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20inside%20Grand%20Bazaar%20with%20colorful%20lamps%20above%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236a81c6ad288d1480c8c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222457%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20glad%20we%20went%20to%20the%20Grand%20Bazaar%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I'd%20bought%20fewer%20things%20there.%20%3Cp%3EAlison%20Kaplan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20loved%20browsing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-inside-istanbuls-grand-bazaar-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGrand%20Bazaar%20in%20Istanbul%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20but%20I%20wish%20I%20hadn't%20bought%20souvenirs%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20famed%20Turkish%20market%20and%20its%20mazes%20of%20different%20stalls%20felt%20overwhelming%20in%20a%20good%20way.%20I%20was%20captivated%20by%20the%20endless%20colors%20of%20Turkish%20textiles%2C%20the%20rich%20smells%20of%20spices%20and%20teas%2C%20and%20the%20banter%20of%20shopkeepers%20trying%20to%20entice%20us%20into%20their%20stores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20bought%20a%20few%20things%20at%20the%20Grand%20Bazaar%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I'd%20held%20out%20on%20shopping%20until%20the%20next%20day%2C%20when%20we%20took%20the%20ferry%20to%20Kadikoy%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Bosphorus.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20found%20many%20of%20the%20same%20wares%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3EKadikoy%20that%20%3Cspan%3EI'd%20seen%20at%20the%20Grand%20Bazaar%2C%20oftentimes%20for%20almost%20a%20tenth%20of%20the%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20also%20would've%20been%20smart%20to%20check%20US%20customs%20regulations%20before%20buying%20souvenirs.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20looking%20through%20glass%20at%20Turkish%20desserts%20and%20sweets%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68236a80c6ad288d1480c8c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20wasn't%20able%20to%20bring%20all%20of%20my%20Turkish%20treats%20and%20groceries%20home.%20%3Cp%3EAlison%20Kaplan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigu