e're%20going%20to%20think%20will%20be%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20EO.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20one%20of%20my%20thoughts%20is%20formulated%20by%20the%20information%20I%20have%20at%20this%20moment.%20But%20what%20happens%20when%20that%20information%20I%20have%20isn't%20just%20what's%20in%20my%20brain%2C%20but%20it's%20everything%20that%20humanity%20has%20ever%20collected%20and%20put%20online%2C%20ever%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Lee%20posed%20%E2%80%94%20how%20different%20would%20an%20interaction%20between%20two%20people%20look%20if%20an%20AI%20could%20feed%20one%20a%20%26quot%3Bcondensed%20blurb%26quot%3B%20of%20information%20about%20the%20other%2C%20after%20it%20was%20finished%20scraping%20their%20entire%20digital%20footprint%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20when%20AI%20literally%20helps%20me%20think%20in%20real%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20way%20that%20humans%20will%20interact%20with%20each%20other%2C%20with%20the%20world%2C%20all%20of%20our%20thoughts%20will%20be%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Cluely%2C%20Lee%20hopes%20to%20get%20people%20used%20to%20what%20he%20believes%20is%20an%20inevitable%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rate%20of%20societal%20progression%20will%20just%20expand%20and%20exponentiate%20significantly%20once%20everyone%20gets%20along%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20we're%20all%20using%20AI%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20what%20Cluely%20hopes%20to%20achieve%2C%20is%20to%20get%20everybody%20used%20to%2C%20'We're%20all%20using%20AI%20now.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Lee%2C%20it's%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20either%20get%20on%20board%20or%20fall%20so%20far%20behind%20you%20can't%20ever%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMass%20adoption%20of%20AI%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20universe%20of%20the%20pro-AI%20class%20completely%20dominating%20the%20anti-AI%20class%20in%20every%20measurable%20and%20imme