-boost-efficiency-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20management%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sometimes%2C%20because%20of%20parenting%20or%20business%20obligations%2C%20I%20could%20only%20take%20one%20or%20two%20classes%3B%20other%20times%2C%20getting%20motivated%20for%20assignments%20was%20difficult%20because%20I%20knew%20I%20didn't%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eneed%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0this%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20few%20years%20to%20finish%2C%20but%20in%202022%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2047%2C%20I%20graduated%20with%20my%20bachelor's%20degree.%20Because%20of%20COVID%20regulations%2C%20there%20was%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduating-college-ceremony-high-school-pandemic-virtual-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egraduation%20ceremony%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20I%20went%20on%20a%20cruise%20with%20my%20family%20to%20celebrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20two%20of%20my%20kids%20have%20gone%20to%20college.%20Another%20son%20tried%20college%20and%20decided%20it%20wasn't%20for%20him%2C%20so%20he%20enrolled%20in%20trade%20school.%20My%20youngest%20two%20are%20still%20in%20high%20school%2C%20but%20I%20expect%20them%20to%20at%20least%20try%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20proof%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20degree%20to%20be%20successful.%20But%20graduating%20fulfilled%20something%20in%20me%20emotionally%20and%20brought%20a%20sense%20of%20calm.%20I%20had%20finally%20finished%20what%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freenrolled-college-as-multimillionaire-with-kids-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747841817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682cce51ac40ae2b0c9e90ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freenrolled-college-as-multimillionaire-with-kids-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20became%20a%20multimillionaire%20even%20thou