ptoms%20reappeared%2C%20and%20she%20fell%20into%20bad%20company.%20She%20got%20into%20smoking.%20Her%20friends%20would%20send%20her%20on%20their%20behalf%20to%20buy%20liquor.%20She%20would%20go%20around%20temples%20leaving%20Rs%20100%20notes.%20When%20we%20heard%2C%20we%20brought%20her%20back%20to%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicha%20refused%20to%20see%20a%20psychiatrist%2C%20and%20her%20parents%20would%20help%20her%20take%20medication%20by%20hiding%20it%20in%20her%20food.%20The%20effects%20began%20taking%20place.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%2030%20years%20since%2C%20and%20Bakhshy%20says%20her%20recovery%20comes%20and%20goes%20in%20phases.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20her%20recovery%20was%20so%20brilliant%20that%20everyone%20was%20sure%20it%20was%20permanent.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20very%20few%20lucky%20ones%20who%20permanently%20recover%20from%20mental%20illnesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20constant%20shift%20between%20remission%20and%20relapse%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20pinpoint%20how%20the%20latter%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richa%20and%20others%20enrolled%20at%20SAA%20during%20a%20dance%20movement%20therapy%20session%20(Credit%3A%20SAA)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1747836831-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436286%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERicha%20and%20others%20enrolled%20at%20SAA%20during%20a%20dance%20movement%20therapy%20session%20(Picture%20source%3A%20SAA)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBakhshy%20says%20that%20when%20Richa%20was%20diagnosed%2C%20their%20entire%20lives%20changed.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20her%20erratic%20behaviour%2C%20relatives%20and%20friends%20stopped%20visiting.%20Neighbours%20became%20fearful%20that%20she%20was%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20children.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20India%2C%20invitations%20are%20addressed%20to%20Mr%2C%20Mrs%2C%20and%20family.%20We%20never%20get%20invites%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98family%E2%80%99.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20leave%20her%20alone%20and%20go%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Since%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20leave%20Richa%20alone%2C%20Bakhshy%E2%80%99s%20wife%20took%20a%20year-long%20leave%20without%20pay%2C%20and%20had%20to%20eventually%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20never%20believed%20in%20rituals.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20never%20let%20Richa%20get%20her%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChudakarana%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emundan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Edone%20when%20she%20was%20a%20baby.%20But%20after%20Richa%20was%20diagnosed%2C%20my%20wife%20wondered%20if%20it%20was%20because%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20conduct%20the%20ceremony.%20We%20decided%20to%20get%20her%20head%20shaved%2C%20but%20Richa%20refused.%20To%20set%20an%20example%2C%20my%20wife%20shaved%20her%20own%20head.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20extent%20she%20went%20to.%20All%20the%20praying%20and%20rituals%20she%20never%20conducted%20in%20her%20entire%20life%2C%20she%20did%20when%20Richa%20became%20sick%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20creation%20of%20a%20safe%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20Bakhshy%20and%20his%20family%20relocated%20to%20Pune.%20%E2%80%9CPune%20and%20Bengaluru%20are%20generally%20better%20equipped%20as%20cities%20for%20the%20mentally%20ill.%20We%20moved%20to%20Pune%20thinking%20that%20Richa%E2%80%99s%20recovery%20might%20be%20easier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20enrolled%20her%20in%20the%20Schizophrenia%20Awareness%20Association.%20We%E2%80%99d%20take%20her%20for%20visits%20during%20the%20day%2C%20and%20while%20she%20was%20in%20the%20rehab%20centre%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20spend%20my%20time%20around%20the%20campus%2C%20reading%20or%20mingling%20with%20the%20people%20there.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20be%20happy%20to%20help%20if%20they%20needed%20any%20assistance.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20was%20Canada-based%20Dr%20Jagannath%20Wani%2C%20whose%20wife%20also%20had%20schizophrenia.%20He%20would%20visit%20India%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20and%20we%20became%20good%20friends.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20offered%20me%20his%20position%20as%20president.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBakhshy%20was%20initially%20hesitant%2C%20given%20that%20there%20were%20many%20who%20had%20worked%20in%20the%20organisation%20before%20him.%20He%20offered%20to%20be%20a%20trustee%20instead%2C%20but%20Wani%20was%20determined.%20In%202010%2C%20Bakhshy%20became%20the%20president%20of%20SAA.%20He%20served%20for%20five%20years%20on%20the%20Institutional%20Board%20of%20NIMHANS%20and%20was%20also%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Hospital%20Management%20Committee%20of%20the%20organisation%20for%20three%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Birthday%20celebrations%20at%20SAA%20(Picture%20source%3A%20SAA)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-association-1-1747836908-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBirthday%20celebrations%20at%20SAA%20(Picture%20source%3A%20SAA)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAA%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20centres%20for%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20the%20mentally%20ill.%20The%20premises%20of%20the%20centre%20were%20expanded%20under%20Bakhshy%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20and%20the%20institute%20started%20a%20centre%20for%20patients%20to%20socialise%20and%20mingle%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%20their%20caregivers%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20jobs%20or%20other%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20residential%20facility%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20that%20patients%20should%20not%20be%20kept%20isolated%20from%20the%20larger%20community.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20bring%20in%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20remain%20home%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20good%20for%20them.%20But%20if%20they%20remain%20away%20from%20their%20families%20for%20too%20long%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20them%20well%20either.%20Humans%20are%20social%20animals%2C%20and%20need%20to%20meet%20other%20people.%20Our%20counsellors%20take%20care%20of%20them%20in%20case%20of%20erratic%20behaviour%2C%20but%20this%20way%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20completely%20shut%20out%20from%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20and%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meantime%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F183217%2Fnayi-disha-community-parents-children-special-needs-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaregivers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0can%20do%20other%20jobs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicha%20was%20this%20centre%E2%80%99s%20first%20patient%2C%20and%20now%20there%20are%2040-50.%20The%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20certainly%20was%20a%20hindrance%2C%20and%20the%20centre%20would%20then%20conduct%20online%20sessions%20for%20its%20patients.%20Bakhshy%20retired%20in%202019%2C%20but%20remains%20involved%20in%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20day-to-day%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20small%2C%20yet%20steady%20step%20forward%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20changes%20needed%20to%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20Mental%20Health%20Act%20of%201987.%20The%20Indian%20Law%20Society%2C%20Pune%2C%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20drafting%20changes%2C%20and%20Bakhshy%2C%20who%20was%20president%20of%20SAA%2C%20was%20involved.%20When%20the%20committee%20noted%20the%20number%20of%20changes%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20made%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20a%20new%20Act%20was%20needed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20Parliament%20in%202013%2C%20and%20Bakhshy%20was%20also%20invited.%20He%20says%20the%20perspective%20of%20human%20rights%20drove%20the%20new%20Act.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20the%20new%20law%20puts%20restrictions%20on%20the%20use%20of%20direct%20ECT%20(electroconvulsive%20therapy).%20The%20treatment%20has%20been%20strictly%20prohibited%20on%20minors.%20The%20law%20dictates%20that%20general%20anaesthesia%20and%20muscle%20relaxants%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20before%20the%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20dictates%20that%20general%20hospitals%20with%20psychiatric%20wards%20need%20to%20go%20through%20a%20registration%20process%20so%20that%20a%20record%20of%20the%20number%20of%20beds%20in%20each%20can%20be%20kept.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%E2%80%99s%20mental%20healthcare%20system%20urgently%20needs%20more%20accessible%20counselling%20and%20rehabilitation%20services%2C%20especially%20for%20caregivers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-7_11zon-1747837581-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436304%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20mental%20healthcare%20system%20urgently%20needs%20more%20accessible%20counselling%20and%20rehabilitation%20services%2C%20especially%20for%20caregivers.%20(Representational%20image%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20criticisms%20for%20this%2C%20which%20said%20that%20many%20general%20and%20government%20hospitals%20would%20close%20down%20these%20wards%20to%20avoid%20going%20through%20the%20process.%20But%20the%20point%20here%20is%20that%20we%20need%20to%20maintain%20records%20for%20statistical%20purposes%2C%20and%20also%20that%20once%20these%20wards%20apply%20for%20registration%2C%20they%20have%20to%20maintain%20the%20standards%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Act%2C%20such%20as%20maintenance%20of%20hygiene%2C%20reduction%20of%20overcrowding%2C%20recreational%20spaces%20for%20patients%2C%20availability%20of%20an%20adequate%20number%20of%20toilets%2C%20sanitary%20pads%20for%20female%20patients%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20aspect%20of%20the%20Act%20that%20was%20not%20included%20after%20protests%20by%20human%20rights%20activists%20was%20the%20independent%20admission%20of%20patients.%20%E2%80%9CSay%20a%20patient%20is%20getting%20violent%2C%20and%20is%20a%20danger%20to%20themselves%20or%20others%20in%20the%20family%20and%20neighbourhood.%20Or%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20care%20for%20themselves.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20can%20be%20admitted%20forcibly%20as%20well.%20But%20the%20activists%20opposed%20this%20forcible%20admission%2C%20while%20we%20caregivers%20supported%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caregivers%20say%20that%20in%20India%2C%20where%20families%20often%20hold%20more%20importance%20than%20personal%20autonomy%2C%20the%20new%20Act%20might%20inhibit%20doctors%20from%20making%20clinical%20decisions%2C%20thus%20shifting%20the%20burden%20on%20the%20former%E2%80%99s%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBakhshy%20also%20says%20that%20despite%20the%20new%20law%2C%20the%20state%20needs%20to%20be%20far%20more%20active%20in%20its%20implementation%20of%20adequate%20facilities%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F147566%2Fcrust-and-core-cafe-kolkata-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ementally%20ill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20swan%20song%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20aspects%20of%20the%20Act%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20included%2C%20but%20the%20changes%20from%20the%20previous%20Act%20are%20still%20monumental%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bakhshy%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%201987%20Act%2C%20the%20mentally%20ill%20in%20India%20were%20governed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Lunacy%20Act%2C%201912.%20This%20was%20a%20British-era%20law.%20The%20Indian%20Psychiatric%20Society%20was%20formed%20in%201947%2C%20and%20it%20took%2040%20years%20before%20the%20next%20Act%20took%20shape.%20So%20we%E2%80%99re%20definitely%20moving%20forward.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20supported%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20remained%20in%20cold%20storage%20for%20a%20while%2C%20as%20the%20government%20changed%20in%202014.%20%E2%80%9COther%20political%20issues%20took%20precedence%20for%20some%20time.%20The%20government%20finally%20picked%20it%20up%20in%202016%2C%20and%20the%20Act%20was%20officially%20passed%20in%202017.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBakhshy%20has%20also%20authored%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20only%20books%20for%20caregivers%20in%202016%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Mental%20Illness%20and%20Caregiving%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20daughter%20fell%20ill%20in%201991%2C%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20even%20heard%20of%20schizophrenia.%20The%20internet%20was%20very%20new%2C%20so%20I%20used%20it%20to%20go%20through%20Wikipedia%20and%20other%20such%20portals%20for%20preliminary%20information.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I%20have%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20and%20experience.%20I%20wanted%20to%20pass%20on%20this%20critical%20knowledge%20to%20other%20families%20with%20similar%20stories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20it%20to%20be%20a%20Bible%20for%20caregivers%20in%20India.%20This%20will%20be%20what%20they%20call%20a%20swan%20song%20%E2%80%94%20my%20parting%20gift%20to%20the%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Yoshita%20Rao%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747837667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Famrit-kumar-bakhshy-1-1-1747836728.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D436280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pune-based%20Amrit%20Kumar%20Bakhshy%2C%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Schizophrenia%20Awareness%20Association%2C%20talks%20about%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20schizophrenia%2C%20his%20book%20on%20caregivers%20in%20India%2C%20and%20his%20role%20in%20helping%20draft%20the%20Mental%20Healthcare%20Act%2C%202017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Divya%20Sethu%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436280%2Ffather-daughter-schizophrenia-mental-health-law-reform-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IndiGo%20Posts%20Highest%20Q4%20Profit%20Of%20Rs%203%2C068%20Crore%20On%20Strong%20Air%20Travel%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%