-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20friends%20and%20neighbours%20visit%2C%20drawn%20by%20the%20vibrant%20blooms%20and%20the%20hushed%20sanctuary%20Afsana%20has%20created%2C%20her%20heart%20swells%20with%20quiet%20triumph.%20%E2%80%9CGuests%20come%20to%20my%20terrace%20and%20take%20selfies%20with%20my%20plants.%20I%20feel%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20succeed%20in%20fulfilling%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20behind%20this%20beauty%20lies%20a%20world%20of%20effort%20and%20experimentation%2C%20especially%20in%20how%20Afsana%20nurtures%20each%20plant%20with%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECompost%20from%20peels%2C%20eggshells%2C%20tea%20leaves%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20days%20were%20a%20struggle.%20Afsana%E2%80%99s%20heart%20was%20heavy%2C%20and%20her%20knowledge%20of%20gardening%20limited.%20She%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20from%20losing%20plants%20in%20scorching%20summer%20days%20to%20temperamental%20varieties%20that%20refused%20to%20bloom.%20However%2C%20each%20plant%20she%20nurtured%20was%20a%20homage%20to%20her%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20kept%20her%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20days%20turned%20into%20weeks%20and%20weeks%20into%20months%2C%20Afsana%E2%80%99s%20terrace%20began%20to%20transform.%20The%20garden%20burgeoned%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20flowering%20plants%20like%20hibiscus%20and%20bougainvillaea%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20like%20%3Cem%3Eanjeer%3C%2Fem%3E%20(figs)%2C%20guava%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eshareefa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(custard%20apple).%20Every%20corner%20of%20the%201%2C500-square-foot%20terrace%