%20world.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fjhansi-gardener-4-1747725984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fjhansi-gardener-4-1747725984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fjhansi-gardener-4-1747725984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fjhansi-gardener-4-1747725984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fjhansi-gardener-4-1747725984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435034%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20garden%20offers%20Afsana%20a%20refuge%20from%20the%20world.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20harvested%20melons%20and%20watermelons.%20They%20were%20so%20sweet%20that%20we%20devoured%20all%20of%20them.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20actually%20plant%20seeds%20for%20these%2C%20yet%20they%20flourished.%20Initially%2C%20there%20were%20fewer%20birds%20around%2C%20but%20now%20many%20flock%20to%20my%20garden%2C%20along%20with%20squirrels.%20They%20seem%20to%20bring%20seeds%20along%2C%20turning%20my%20garden%20into%20a%20place%20of%20surprising%20growth%20and%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98She%20lives%20through%20every%20flower%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20garden%20offers%20Afsana%20a%20refuge%20from%20the%20world%2C%20a%20place%20where%20the%20stresses%20of%20life%20fade%20amidst%20the%20whispering%20leaves.%20Her%20elder%20son%2C%20Mohd%20Zaqi%20Ansari%20(25)%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sudden%20loss%20of%20my%20sister%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age%20left%20my%20mother%20in%20a%20profound%20state%20of%20loneliness%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%20Despite%20the%20heavy%20grief%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20determined%