%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20energy%20dips%2C%20I%20remind%20myself%20of%20how%20far%20I%20have%20come.%20This%20is%20not%20something%20I%20was%20born%20with.%20It%20is%20the%20result%20of%20showing%20up%20every%20day%2C%20even%20on%20the%20hard%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2057-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Learn%20to%20balance%20duties%20and%20dreams%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother-turned-fitness%20influencer%20faced%20resistance%20early%20on.%20%E2%80%9CNeighbours%20would%20comment%20if%20I%20skipped%20chores%20for%20the%20gym%2C%20or%20if%20my%20house%20was%20not%20perfectly%20tidy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20put%20my%20foot%20down.%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20non-negotiable%20for%20me.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20She%20also%20fought%20the%20ingrained%20belief%20that%20a%20mother%20must%20always%20sacrifice%20for%20the%20family%2C%20and%20nothing%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20taught%20that%20if%20kids%20have%20exams%2C%20we%20give%20up%20everything.%20But%20if%20we%20have%20an%20exam%20or%20want%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20it%20is%20silly.%20That%20is%20the%20stereotype%20I%20wanted%20to%20break%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Ashu%20lives%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20balances%20content%20creation%2C%20brand%20collaborations%2C%20and%20family%20life%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20inspire%20thousands.%20Her%20daily%20content%20reaches%20people%20across%20India%2C%20with%20messages%20on%20fitness%2C%20ageing%2C%20and%20food%2C%20rooted%20in%20her%20upbringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20eating%20parathas.%20I%20cannot%20suddenly%20switch%20to%20oats.%20So%20I%20tweak%20desi%20food%20and%20make%20it%20healthy.%20That%20is%20why%20people%20love%20my%20recipes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20She%20also%20teaches%20her%20granddaughter%20to%20enjoy%20%E2%80%98me%20time%2C%E2%80%99%20because%20independence%20starts%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C