s%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20entrepreneurs%20or%20C-suite%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20to%20take%20actionable%20steps%20forward.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20I%20called%20for%20a%20mindset%20shift%3A%20we%20must%20all%20embrace%20a%20culture%20of%20learning%2C%20unlearning%2C%20and%20relearning%20if%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20fast-evolving%20landscape%20of%20Industry%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20moment%20to%20build%20bridges%2C%20not%20barriers%2C%20for%20SMEs%20stepping%20into%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20digitally%20empowered%20future.%20And%20I%E2%80%99m%20committed%20to%20helping%20make%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20collaboration%20matters%20now%20more%20than%20ever%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20local%20action%20and%20community-led%20change%20are%20powerful%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20realised%20that%20big%20impact%20often%20needs%20big%20collaboration.%20Climate%20change%2C%20water%20stress%2C%20and%20digital%20divides%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20borders%E2%80%94and%20the%20solutions%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20either.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20regional%20cooperation%20is%20becoming%20such%20a%20critical%20piece%20of%20the%20sustainability%20puzzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20stepping%20up%20to%20play%20a%20bigger%20role%E2%80%94not%20just%20for%20itself%2C%20but%20as%20a%20connector%20between%20regions.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20Europe%2C%20or%20Africa%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20building%20bridges%20that%20align%20with%20climate%20goals%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20shared%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EConnecting%20with%20the%20Mediterranean%3A%20A%20conversation%20that%20stayed%20with%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20India-Mediterranean%20Business%20Conclave%202024%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20I%20saw%20first-hand%20how%20this%20vision%20is%20taking%20shape.%20The%20room%20was%20filled%20w