aboration%20offers%20a%20powerful%20model%20for%20shared%20resilience%2C%20knowledge%20exchange%2C%20and%20inclusive%2C%20low-carbon%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20region%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20impacts%20such%20as%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20BIMSTEC%20offers%20a%20platform%20to%20synchronise%20policies%2C%20mobilise%20resources%2C%20and%20share%20knowledge%2C%20strengthening%20collective%20resilience%20and%20sustainable%20development%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20bridging%20national%20priorities%20with%20regional%20strategies%2C%20BIMSTEC%20is%20not%20just%20fostering%20economic%20cooperation%20but%20also%20pioneering%20pathways%20toward%20a%20climate-resilient%20and%20environmentally%20sustainable%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%202024%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Dr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%20engaged%20with%20delegates%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20other%20member%20nations%2C%20exploring%20opportunities%20for%20regional%20cooperation%20and%20development.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1