-featured-image-2025-05-19T170115.385_11zon-1-1747654351-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170115.385_11zon-1-1747654351-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170115.385_11zon-1-1747654351-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170115.385_11zon-1-1747654351-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434314%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIncubators%20like%20IIT%20Madras%20Research%20Park%20offer%20critical%20testbeds%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20startups%20to%20pilot%20and%20scale%20real-world%20innovations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIP%20and%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20to%20touch%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20filing%20and%20defending%20intellectual%20property%20(IP)%E2%80%94a%20complex%20process%20that%20many%20innovators%20struggle%20with.%20While%20the%20legal%20framework%20is%20in%20place%2C%20the%20system%20still%20needs%20to%20evolve%20to%20meet%20the%20pace%20of%20innovation%2C%20especially%20in%20high-tech%20and%20emerging%20sectors.%20India%20currently%20ranks%2040th%20out%20of%2053%20countries%20in%20the%20International%20IP%20Index.%20This%20indicates%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20for%20improvement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Gopalika%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CStrong%20IP%20protection%20is%20not%20just%20about%20legal%20rights.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20key%20enabler%20for%20innovation%20and%20also%20investments.%20When%20startups%20are%20confident%20that%20their%20ideas%20are%20protected%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20willing%20to%20take%20bold%20risks.%20Meanwhile%2C%20for%20investors%2C%20a%20clear%20and%20enforceable%20IP%20strategy%20is%20often%20a%20sign%20of%20credibility%20and%20long-term%20value.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20state%20of%20IP%20laws%20in%20India%20is%20fraught%20with%20friction.%20%E2%80%9CWeak%20IP%20protection%20and%20enforcement%20mechanisms%20continue%20to%20impede%20innovation%20and%20technology%20transfer%20within%20this%20entire%20ecosystem.%20In%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20companies%20with%20strong%20patent%20portfolios%20are%20often%20more%20attractive%20because%20patents%20can%20be%20leveraged%20for%20licensing%20agreements%20or%20strategic%20partnerships%20or%20even%20as%20defensive%20assets%20against%20competitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20can%20the%20government%20do%20to%20fill%20this%20gap%20in%20funding%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20in%20climate%20tech%20investment%2C%20there%20are%20specific%20risks%20and%20financial%20gaps%20that%20are%20holding%20capital%20back.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20the%20government%20can%20do%20to%20address%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPublic%20finance%20institutions%20and%20government-backed%20funds%20have%20a%20key%20role%20in%20addressing%20these%20issues.%20They%20can%20provide%20vital%20funding%20for%20early-stage%20research%20and%20development%20and%20testing%20new%20technologies%2C%20and%20also%20taking%20on%20the%20risky%20paths%20that%20private%20investors%20often%20avoid.%20Governments%20can%20also%20help%20startups%20during%20their%20commercialisation%20phase%20by%20offering%20financial%20incentives%20and%20reducing%20certain%20investment%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gopalika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20I%20think%20creating%20a%20strong%20climate%20tech%20innovation%20framework%20that%20includes%20clear%20policies%2C%20support%20for%20pricing%20mechanisms%2C%20and%20also%20integration%20of%20climate%20tech%20into%20national%20economic%20planning%20is%20very%20essential.%20These%20actions%20can%20build%20a%20supportive%20ecosystem%20that%20will%20drive%20faster%20adoption%20of%20these%20low-carbon%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20Bansal%2C%20Founding%20Partner%20at%20Avaana%20Capital%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20firm%20that%20focuses%20on%20investing%20in%20climate%20tech%20startups%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20powerful%20role%20the%20government%20can%20play%20is%20that%20of%20market%20enabler.%20Early-stage%20climate%20tech%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20need%20funding%E2%80%94it%20needs%20demand%20signals%2C%20regulatory%20clarity%2C%20and%20outcome-linked%20incentives%20that%20make%20markets%20viable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20sector%20poised%20for%20growth%2C%20better%20venture%20debt%20and%20blended%20finance%20could%20unlock%20scalable%2C%20inclusive%20impact%20across%20the%20economy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T170330.214_11zon-1747654434-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20sector%20poised%20for%20growth%2C%20better%20venture%20debt%20and%20blended%20finance%20could%20unlock%20scalable%2C%20inclusive%20impact%20across%20the%20economy.%20(Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20this%20work%20with%20EPR%20(extended%20producer%20responsibility)%20helping%20consolidate%20the%20circularity%20sector%20and%20the%20PLI%20(production-linked%20incentive)%20scheme%20helping%20accelerate%20renewable%20energy%20and%20EV%20adoption.%20We%20now%20need%20similar%20frameworks%20for%20new%20sectors%E2%80%94like%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20alternate%20materials%2C%20or%20circular%20economy%20infrastructure.%20Long-term%20procurement%20policies%2C%20interoperable%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20performance%20benchmarking%20can%20dramatically%20lower%20perceived%20risk%20and%20attract%20private%20capital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20step%20governments%20can%20also%20take%20is%20to%20lift%20the%20roadblocks%20standing%20in%20the%20way%20of%20global%20capital.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20roadblocks%20here%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20standardised%20frameworks%20that%20allow%20international%20investors%20to%20assess%20and%20trust%20the%20climate%20impact%20of%20these%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20critical%20to%20develop%20a%20robust%20climate-aligned%20taxonomy%2C%20one%20that%20clearly%20defines%20what%20qualifies%20as%20a%20green%20or%20climate%20investment%20across%20various%20industries.%20It%20will%20be%20very%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20particular%20taxonomy%20is%20not%20just%20aligned%20with%20international%20standards%2C%20but%20is%20also%20tailored%20to%20the%20very%20unique%20needs%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20ecosystem.%20In%20India%2C%20we%20have%20green%20finance%2C%20climate%20finance%2C%20adaptation%20finance%2C%20mitigation%20and%20transition%20finance%2C%20and%20there%20is%20also%20something%20called%20loss%20and%20damage%20finance%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gopalika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20terms%20with%20no%20clear%20definition%20of%20what%20constitutes%20green%20investment%20or%20climate%20investments.%20When%20there%20is%20no%20standardised%20taxonomy%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20for%20global%20investors%20to%20navigate%20our%20ecosystem%20and%20ensure%20that%20these%20flows%20are%20truly%20going%20towards%20impactful%20solutions.%20A%20robust%20climate-aligned%20taxonomy%20is%20very%20important%20for%20all%20the%20sectors%20that%20are%20there%20in%20climate%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20grant%20capital%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20tool%20in%20unlocking%20funding%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20is%20developing%20a%20robust%20grant%20capital%20infrastructure.%20In%20layman%E2%80%99s%20terms%2C%20grant%20capital%20infrastructure%20refers%20to%20public%20or%20philanthropic%20funding%20used%20to%20build%20the%20foundational%20systems%20that%20support%20innovation%2C%20particularly%20in%20sectors%20like%20climate%20tech%2C%20where%20private%20investments%20may%20be%20slow%20or%20cautious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrant%20capital%20infrastructure%20is%20about%20using%20non-commercial%20funds%20to%20create%20physical%20and%20institutional%20support%20systems%20that%20help%20innovations%20grow.%20The%20government%20might%20use%20certain%20grant%20funding%20to%20set%20up%20a%20battery%20lab%20or%20an%20EV%20charge%20prototype%20zone.%20This%20is%20a%20way%20of%20de-risking%20the%20ecosystem%20so%20private%20investors%20feel%20more%20confident%20backing%20startups%20later.%20While%20India%20has%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20venture%20capital%20and%20private%20equity%20funding%2C%20many%20early-stage%20climate%20innovators%20lack%20access%20to%20non-dilutive%20grant%20capital%20essential%20for%20research%20and%20development%2C%20testing%20initial%20proof%20of%20concept%20and%20supply%20chain%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gopalika.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20this%20grant%20capital%20infrastructure%20would%20provide%20much-needed%20support%20for%20climate%20projects%20in%20their%20initial%20stages.%20It%20will%20also%20help%20startups%20to%20de-risk%20their%20technologies%20before%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20private%20investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountries%20like%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20stand%20out%20for%20their%20structured%2C%20non-dilutive%20grant%20support%20to%20climate%20innovation.%20In%20Japan%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Economy%2C%20Trade%20and%20Industry%20(METI)%20has%20launched%20the%20Green%20Innovation%20Fund%2C%20worth%20%C2%A52%20trillion%2C%20administered%20by%20the%20New%20Energy%20and%20Industrial%20Technology%20Development%20Organization%20(NEDO).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20fund%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20sustained%2C%20long-term%20support%E2%80%94over%20a%2010-year%20horizon%E2%80%94for%20companies%20pursuing%20ambitious%20climate%20innovation%20goals.%20It%20supports%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20from%20R%26amp%3BD%20to%20demonstration%20and%20eventual%20deployment.%20Such%20initiatives%20reflect%20the%20role%20of%20grant%20capital%20not%20merely%20as%20funding%2C%20but%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20creating%20the%20physical%20and%20institutional%20ecosystems%20that%20early-stage%20technologies%20need%20to%20thrive.%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is%20a%20compelling%20example%20of%20how%20non-commercial%20capital%20can%20be%20used%20to%20de-risk%20innovation%20and%20accelerate%20the%20commercialisation%20of%20deep-tech%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20startups%20often%20lack%20access%20to%20institutional%20support%2C%20regulatory%20clarity%2C%20and%20scale-up%20capital%2C%20which%20can%20stall%20breakthrough%20ideas.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165636.901_11zon-1747654016-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20startups%20often%20lack%20access%20to%20institutional%20support%2C%20regulatory%20clarity%2C%20and%20scale-up%20capital%2C%20which%20can%20stall%20breakthrough%20ideas.%20(Representative%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20broader%20grant%20capital%20infrastructure%20is%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98blended%20finance%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20specifically%20addresses%20a%20startup%E2%80%99s%20need%20for%20consistent%20funding%20and%20investor%20anxiety.%20Blended%20finance%20refers%20to%20using%20public%20money%20from%20government%20donors%20alongside%20private%20money%20from%20investors%2C%20reducing%20the%20risk%2C%20and%20encouraging%20more%20funding%20into%20climate%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20the%20government%20covers%20part%20of%20the%20risk%2C%20a%20private%20investor%20might%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20fund%20a%20solar%20project.%20For%20this%20to%20work%20well%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20take%20steps%20like%20simplifying%20taxes%20on%20green%20investments%20and%20creating%20clear%20rules%20for%20what%20counts%20as%20green%20finance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKenya%E2%80%99s%20Renewable%20Energy%20Fund%20is%20a%20good%20model%20for%20blended%20finance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20great%20example%20of%20how%20blended%20finance%20can%20work%2C%20especially%20for%20projects%20like%20solar%20energy.%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20Renewable%20Energy%20Fund%20combines%20donor%20contributions%20with%20private%20investment%20to%20support%20solar%20projects%2C%20thus%20highlighting%20the%20potential%20of%20blended%20finance%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20catalysing%20climate%20innovation%20and%20scaling%20impactful%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Gopalika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20promising%20example%20from%20India%20is%20IFC%E2%80%99s%20recent%20commitment%20to%20the%20Omnivore%20Agritech%20%26amp%3B%20Climate%20Sustainability%20Fund%203%20(%E2%80%9COmnivore%20III%E2%80%9D)%2C%20where%20it%20is%20investing%20up%20to%20%2412%20million%20in%20equity.%20This%20venture%20capital%20fund%20focuses%20on%20AgriTech%20and%20FoodTech%20startups%20in%20India%2C%20including%20companies%20with%20operations%20across%20Southeast%20Asia.%20The%20initiative%20demonstrates%20how%20blended%20finance%20can%20help%20unlock%20greater%20private%20sector%20capital%20for%20climate-smart%20agriculture%E2%80%94an%20area%20critical%20to%20both%20climate%20adaptation%20and%20economic%20resilience%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESecuring%20affordable%20venture%20debt%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAffordable%20venture%20debt%20provides%20a%20helpful%20way%20to%20boost%20the%20growth%20of%20climate%20tech%20companies%2C%20especially%20those%20that%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20operate%2C%20like%20renewable%20energy%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20battery%20recycling.%20Think%20of%20affordable%20venture%20debt%20as%20a%20way%20for%20startups%20to%20raise%20money%20without%20giving%20up%20ownership.%20It%E2%80%99s%20tailored%20for%20young%20companies%20that%20may%20not%20yet%20have%20steady%20profit%20streams%20or%20assets%20to%20show%20to%20traditional%20banks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20traditional%20bank%20loans%2C%20venture%20debt%20features%20flexible%20terms%20on%20repayments%20and%20less%20emphasis%20on%20traditional%20collateral%2Fassets.%20The%20path%20to%20profits%20is%20very%20long%2C%20and%20many%20investors%20get%20nervous%20about%20the%20wait.%20Venture%20debt%20can%20step%20in%20to%20fill%20this%20critical%20gap%20and%20offer%20non-dilutive%20capital%20to%20startups.%20This%20allows%20startups%20to%20build%2C%20test%20and%20grow%20without%20constantly%20chasing%20equity%20funding%20or%20giving%20away%20parts%20of%20their%20company.%20Affordable%20debt%20can%20be%20a%20smart%20bridge%20between%20early%20innovation%20and%20long-term%20commercial%20success%2C%20helping%20startups%20survive%20the%20Valley%20of%20Death%20and%20become%20strong%20enough%20to%20attract%20bigger%20investments%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnlocking%20demand%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20customers%20such%20as%20hospitals%2C%20Fast%20Moving%20Consumer%20Goods%20(FMCG)%20companies%2C%20and%20manufacturers%20are%20hesitant%20to%20adopt%20climate%20solutions%20due%20to%20the%20perceived%20cost%20premiums%20and%20operational%20uncertainties.%20How%20can%20we%20unlock%20their%20demand%20for%20these%20solutions%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlocking%20demand%20from%20large%20companies%20is%20very%20critical%20to%20scale%20in%20these%20climate%20tech%20startups.%20The%20hesitation%20from%20FMCG%20companies%20and%20large%20entities%20often%20boils%20down%20to%20two%20things%3A%20perceived%20high%20cost%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20operational%20disruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20according%20to%20Gopalika%2C%20we%20need%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20De-risk%20the%20adoption%3A%20The%20government%20and%20private%20financial%20institutions%20can%20step%20in%20with%20guarantees%20and%20pilot%20programmes%2C%20and%20adoption%20subsidies%20that%20offset%20these%20initial%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Standardised%20evaluation%20frameworks%3A%20We%20need%20clear%20and%20transparent%20systems%20to%20measure%20a%20startup%E2%80%99s%20technology%20or%20technical%20feasibility%2C%20their%20cost%20efficiency%2C%20scalability%20and%20environmental%20impact%2C%20and%20this%20helps%20larger%20players%20make%20confident%20and%20informed%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Recognise%20value%20beyond%20revenue%3A%20Many%20climate%20tech%20solutions%2C%20especially%20hardware-based%20ones%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20show%20quick%20profits.%20They%20bring%20long-term%20value%20in%20terms%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20IP%20and%20environmental%20compliance.%20So%2C%20if%20we%20create%20systems%20that%20account%20for%20this%20value%2C%20both%20corporations%20and%20investors%20would%20start%20looking%20at%20these%20companies%20a%20bit%20differently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20We%20need%20to%20establish%20stronger%20B2B%20partnerships.%20We%20need%20mechanisms%20that%20bring%20startups%20and%20large%20corporations%20into%20structured%20dialogues%20or%20co-development%20spaces%2C%20where%20new%20technologies%20can%20be%20piloted%20safely%20and%20iteratively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20large%20companies%20begin%20adopting%20and%20validating%20the%20solution%2C%20it%20builds%20trust%2C%20and%20it%20also%20shows%20investors%20that%20there%20is%20real%20market%20demand%20and%20scalability%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20increases%20funding%20and%20funding%20opportunities%20for%20these%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20long-term%20funding%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%2C%20these%20are%20some%20of%20the%20steps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken.%20It%20will%20require%20extensive%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20between%20startups%2C%20private%20investors%20and%20the%20government%2C%20but%20as%20economies%20like%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20have%20shown%2C%20this%20is%20possible.%20Once%20we%20unlock%20greater%20funding%20for%20climatech%20startups%2C%20India%20will%20be%20in%20a%20much%20stronger%20place%20to%20mitigate%20the%20risks%20and%20challenges%20associated%20with%20climate%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%20and%20Tanaya%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747654999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D434253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%202.5%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20startups%20reach%20growth-stage%20funding.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20why%20long-term%20investment%2C%20better%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20patient%20capital%20are%20key%20to%20scaling%20impact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F434253%2Findia-climate-tech-startup-funding-challenges%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Marol%20Turned%20a%20Barren%20Plot%20into%20a%203.5-Acre%20Urban%20Forest%20That%20Cools%20the%20Area%20by%204%C2%B0C%22